 -my project is about personal diary Management system.
 -on hearing the title we may think
 it is just like ordinary diary
 but actualy it is not like that
 -this is very useful concept for us.
 we can use this to record our day to day activites,
 can be used to note down imp meetings, dates, travelling plans, memories, etc.
 it is very very useful one.
 for eg:
 stu-homewrks,timetables
 doctor-meetings,operations,conference
 traveller-journey date/day/time,things to be packed,memoeries
 homemakers-grocery list,daily expenses,monthly expenses.
 it is user friendly one and it’s not time consuming.
 user can daily,update,delete or just look on the files.

highlights/Features:
-Proper Log-In Systems.
-Proper Validations.
-Password Protected and Password System in Each Sections.
-High Security.

key feature is
There’s maximum privacy to the recorded files.
it is a password protected one
each section is password Protected
and contain high security so there is no chance for data loss.
we can change password as many times we need.

